<sect2>
<title>Installation de scrollkeeper</title>

<para>Installez scrollkeeper en lançant les commandes suivantes:</para>

<para><screen><userinput>./configure --prefix=/opt/gnome2 --sysconfdir=/etc --localstatedir=/var --disable-static \
--with-omfdirs=/usr/share/omf:/opt/gnome/share/omf:/opt/kde/share/omf:/opt/gnome2/share/omf &amp;&amp;
make &amp;&amp;
make install </userinput></screen></para>

</sect2>

